General.Name: Coda Minerals Ltd
General.Description: Coda Minerals Limited, an exploration company, focuses on the exploration, discovery, and development of minerals in the base metals, precious metals, and battery minerals sector. The company holds 100% interest in the Elizabeth Creek copper project covering an area of 701 square kilometers located in South Australia; and Cameron River Copper Gold project covering an area of 35 square kilometers located in Queensland. Coda Minerals Limited was incorporated in 2018 and is based in West Perth, Australia.
